      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im 20 weeks pregnant and i have this really bad sinus infection that wont go away. my head is pounding and i cant breathe through my nose at all. i was gonna take some Sudafed but i wasnt sure if that was okay? or maybe some of those strong antibiotics my husband takes for his infections, would those work for a sinus thing?",
